import React from "react"
import { Text, View, Button, ScrollView , TouchableOpacity} from "react-native"
import Header from "./Header"
import Card from "./Card"
import Footer from "./Footer"

export default function Home() {
    return (
        <View>

            <Header />
            <ScrollView >
<TouchableOpacity >
<Card />
</TouchableOpacity>
                
                <Card />
                <Card />
                <Card />
               
            </ScrollView>
            <Footer/>
        </View>
    )
}
